title: Corrigendum to ‘Effects of RG7652, a Monoclonal Antibody Against PCSK9, on Low-Density Lipoprotein Cholesterol (LDL-C), LDL-C Subfractions, and Inflammatory Biomarkers in Patients at High Risk of or with Established Coronary Heart Disease (From the Phase 2 EQUATOR Study)’ The American Journal of Cardiology 119 (2017) 1576–1583
